Sudoku is a logic-based number-placement puzzle. The objective is to fill a 9×9 grid with digits so that each column, each row, and each of the nine 3×3 sub-grids that compose the grid contains all of the digits from 1 to 9. 

Game Features:
- No Ads
- Free Game
- 6000 Sudoku puzzles
- 6 difficulty levels - Beginner, Easy, Normal, Hard, Expert, Legend
- Auto-save & Resume
- Undo function
- Smart Notes 
- Error checking (incorrect entry highlighting)
- Selected digit highlighting
- Including fastest times 



And more much more;

This game uses the code of OpenSudoku and complies with it's license.
The INTERNET permission is required for competitions and game results upload. 
